完成了54次帽子戲法，也在面對153個不同對手時都有入球入賬，而被C.朗拿度破門次數最多的球隊，正是西甲勁旅西維爾（被C.朗拿度攻入27球）。<br />\n<br />\n  C.朗拿度700球詳細分佈如下：<br />\n<br />\n  一、球會：811場605球<br />\n<br />\n  歐聯：164場127球<br />\n<br />\n  英超：196場84球<br />\n<br />\n  西甲：292場311球<br />\n<br />\n  意甲：37場24球<br />\n<br />\n  葡超：25場3球<br />\n<br />\n  西班牙盃：30場22球<br />\n<br />\n  足總盃：26場13球<br />\n<br />\n  聯賽盃：12場4球<br />\n<br />\n  意大利盃：2場0球<br />\n<br />\n  葡萄牙杯：2場2球<br />\n<br />\n  西班牙超級盃：7場4球<br />\n<br />\n  社區盾：1場0球<br />\n<br />\n  意大利超級盃：1場1球<br />\n<br />\n  世冠盃：8場7球<br />\n<br />\n  歐聯資格賽：4場1球<br />\n<br />\n  歐霸盃：2場0球<br />\n<br />\n  歐洲超級盃：2場2球<br />\n<br />\n  二、國家隊：162場95球<br />\n<br />\n  世界盃：17場7球<br />\n<br />\n  世界盃外圍賽：38場30球<br />\n<br />\n  歐國盃：21場9球<br />\n<br />\n  歐國盃外圍賽：33場27球<br />\n<br />\n  洲際國家盃：4場2球<br />\n<br />\n  歐國聯：2場3球<br />\n<br />\n  友誼賽：47場17球"},{"pid":"2b28a77da84463a3972932c8168ec660c41a11ed","tid":1655082,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bcaefe90f45053076c1c80f10125e0329762ef9","tid":1655082,"uid":19552,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:14:59.000Z","msg":"美斯用手入過波 牙朗試過未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1baa3534c56144ec75d2ab47b9ea4c52223b993","tid":1655082,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0bcaefe90f45053076c1c80f10125e0329762ef9","tid":1655082,"uid":19552,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:14:59.000Z","msg":"美斯用手入過波 牙朗試過未"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T03:05:26.000Z","msg":"上帝先得"},{"pid":"eaecce47da9142b0a79ceeda715d9a88ca701673","tid":1655082,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1baa3534c56144ec75d2ab47b9ea4c52223b993","tid":1655082,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0bcaefe90f45053076c1c80f10125e0329762ef9","tid":1655082,"uid":19552,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T